:::: Question 1 ::::
Power of 2

problem statement:::
https://practice.geeksforgeeks.org/problems/power-of-2-1587115620/1?fbclid=IwAR0TwNzfVNI-uFeiavKLFbwiPJgbLnnecWuIvOdEuDKT9kPimjAxu2kkhes

:::: Solution ::::

bool isPowerofTwo(long long n){
        
        if(n == 0)
            return false;
        return !(n & (n - 1));
        
    }
    
